07.000Z","msg":"達哥七宗罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 出賣 back up佬<br />\n<br />\n自己老番完人再屌人老番佢 好撚無恥<br />\n<br />\n早期你未紅 back up 佬冇錢收幫你宣傳又唔撚見你出聲<br />\n<br />\n利用完人就過橋抽板 唔該都冇聲<br />\n<br />\n2. 用老番window<br />\n<br />\n比兄弟踢爆用老番window<br />\n現場live果陣仲死撐扮傻仔話&lsquo;點解會咁？&lsquo;<br />\n之後見勢色唔對同兜唔到就扮晒死狗發文道歉<br />\n<br />\n3. 偷人潮文讀<br />\n<br />\n之前有個潮文作者話過有問題<br />\n達哥未得作者批准就用人地作品做商業用途<br />\n<br />\n4. 打機唔係為錢<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母打撚到搬去康城<br />\n收錢打埋d垃圾game <br />\n又話打機唔係為錢 自打嘴巴<br />\n<br />\n5. 奶共 ，親中，黃絲變藍絲<br />\n<br />\n入左中國公司之後<br />\n逢親大是大非都唔敢出聲<br />\n（黃之峰坐監，立法會投票）<br />\n<br />\n收淘寶錢雙十一買廣告就識！<br />\n<br />\n6. 成日用蝗語 同 人口filter<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔洗講啦 向班小學雞洗腦"},{"pid":"d01a7e02a8f194e08c11ef20aeb0fd9aad2ce59b","tid":1155422,"uid":134012,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.menclub.life/images/image/133/13377929.jpg?t=1543480803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.life%2Fimages%2Fimage%2F133%2F13377929.jpg%3Ft%3D1543480803&h=1b5292bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反轉豬肚就係屎<br />\n紅咗唔認兄弟"},{"pid":"fddf6beb9832b944635af4d202d07d6eb1d07626","tid":1155422,"uid":134012,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:09:48.000Z","msg":"打機達人達哥﹕打機 都可以有出息 我想導人向善，改變世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/080233_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F080233_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=cbbb17f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同奧柏中國合作賣港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c09d312239dc69dc57dda92086ac03f7c95320","tid":1155422,"uid":134012,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T03:12:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MAOE-ACpU4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMAOE-ACpU4w&d=UmPnmdD3xn3